{"tid":741113,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"比人話偷食腳踏兩船唔認 終於自爆了","createTime":"2018-07-13T11:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T16:38:47.000Z","uid":194565,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4850f1663be73bfd7233ffbbe95da1979c89f437","tid":741113,"uid":194565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最慘一定比佢綠過嘅仔<br />\n家下又同返個偷食男一齊 原來自己都係偷食者<br />\n話無一腳踏兩船同討厭人做小三<br />\n16年4月先同前男友影結婚相<br />\n16年5月又話最愛前男友 <br />\n家下先18年7月就同現仼一齊2.5年<br />\n條數唔知點計呢<br />\n<br />\n係港航嘅都知佢返工同人粗口大吵比港航炒左啦<br />\n仲成日拍片當自己係空姐咩<br />\n<br />\n偷食都可以再擺被綠男友d相係fb精選封面<br />\n偷食大大聲表表者 <br />\n<br />\n之前都有巴打有佢黑歷史 罕有有圖有真相<br />\n齊數黑歷史<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/153116_37c19d028320b4bc6aaf9ba2a14c47a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F153116_37c19d028320b4bc6aaf9ba2a14c47a6.png&h=1c29dae0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/153118_5c5758743e3fe8fd5a64d3a89a8fff51.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F153118_5c5758743e3fe8fd5a64d3a89a8fff51.png&h=8053a232&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/153119_eeaef0650374aecc89d68d03de27b72f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F153119_eeaef0650374aecc89d68d03de27b72f.png&h=e543824b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/153122_35dff541d646068d118abee6088ebc50.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F153122_35dff541d646068d118abee6088ebc50.png&h=67da4cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/153123_a0ed1f2ec085e53a68693a19a4bac45e.png\" data-thumbna